1.  In the [Exceptions ]{.Emphasis}area, click [Create
    exception]{.Emphasis}.

2.  In the Create an exception page, provide a name for the exception.

    ::: note
    An access request must meet all of the conditions within a single
    exception. If you have more than one scenario where you don\'t want
    the defined approval method to apply, create separate exceptions for
    each use case.
    :::
